248
00:20:25.569 --> 00:20:26.769
Tadi pagi kita bertemu.

249
00:20:26.769 --> 00:20:28.039
Sebentar lagi, hari peringatan kematian Soo Man,

250
00:20:28.440 --> 00:20:29.940
jadi, aku membeli gula-gula.

251
00:20:30.269 --> 00:20:31.410
Benarkah?

252
00:20:33.880 --> 00:20:36.680
Kakakmu akan menyukainya.

253
00:20:36.680 --> 00:20:37.680
Ya.

254
00:20:38.579 --> 00:20:41.650
Selagi membelikan dia gula-gula,

255
00:20:42.690 --> 00:20:45.089
aku tiba-tiba merasa kasihan kepadanya.

256
00:20:46.019 --> 00:20:47.690
Meskipun Yeo Cheon lebih muda,

257
00:20:48.089 --> 00:20:49.890
dia menikah sebelum Boo Cheon.

258
00:20:49.890 --> 00:20:51.299
Kamu kenal wanita yang baik?

259
00:20:51.559 --> 00:20:52.759
Carilah wanita yang baik.

260
00:20:53.799 --> 00:20:55.630
Jangan sampai dia melajang selamanya.

261
00:20:55.630 --> 00:20:56.700
Baiklah.

262
00:20:57.900 --> 00:20:59.799
Ayah bilang,

263
00:21:00.099 --> 00:21:02.809
putri pemilik perusahaan surat kabar cocok untuk Yeo Cheon.

264
00:21:03.440 --> 00:21:05.740
Ayah punya saran untuknya?

265
00:21:14.589 --> 00:21:17.490
"Mo Hyun"

266
00:21:39.539 --> 00:21:43.579
"Pil Joo"

