00:22:47.450 --> 00:22:50.210
"Jang Kook Hwan"

270
00:22:50.880 --> 00:22:52.750
"Hasil pemeriksaan kesehatan"

271
00:22:55.789 --> 00:22:59.819
"Harus rutin berolahraga. Secara umum, sehat"

